# QuantDSS — Full Implementation Walkthrough

## Summary

Built the entire **QuantDSS** monorepo — **112 files** across 5 phases covering backend, frontend, Docker, and infrastructure.

---

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Broker WebSocket"] --> B["Tick Normaliser"]
    B --> C["Candle Aggregator"]
    C --> D["Strategy Runner"]
    D --> E["EMA Crossover"]
    D --> F["RSI Mean Reversion"]
    E --> G["Risk Engine (7 Rules)"]
    F --> G
    G --> H["Signal Pipeline"]
    H --> I["PostgreSQL/TimescaleDB"]
    H --> J["Alert Dispatcher"]
    J --> K["Telegram Bot"]
    J --> L["SSE → Dashboard"]
```

---

## Phase-by-Phase Summary

### Phase 1 — Foundation
| Component | Files | Key Items |
|-----------|-------|-----------|
| Root configs | 8 | Docker Compose (6 services), Makefile, Nginx, [.env.example](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/.env.example) |
| Core modules | 6 | config, database, redis, security, logging, scheduler |
| Models | 9 | 11 DB tables inc. TimescaleDB hypertable |
| Schemas | 8 | Symbol, Strategy, Candle, Signal, Trade, Risk, Backtest, Auth |
| Migrations | 6 | Raw SQL: tables, hypertable, compression policies |
| API | 13 | FastAPI app factory, deps, 11 routers |
| Ingestion | 8 | Broker adapters (Shoonya, Angel, yfinance), tick normaliser, candle aggregator |
| Scripts | 2 | Seed defaults, bulk historical download |
| Frontend | 12 | Next.js 14, TailwindCSS, Sidebar, Header, 6 page stubs |

### Phase 2 — Core Engine
- [indicators.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/engine/indicators.py) — pandas-ta indicator engine
- [ema_crossover.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/engine/strategies/ema_crossover.py) — Golden/death cross + volume confirmation
- [rsi_mean_reversion.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/engine/strategies/rsi_mean_reversion.py) — Oversold bounce + overbought rejection
- [risk_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/engine/risk_engine.py) — 7-rule fail-fast chain
- [test_risk_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/tests/unit/test_risk_engine.py) — 30+ unit tests

### Phase 3 — Signal Pipeline
- [telegram_notifier.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/alerts/telegram_notifier.py) — Signal/halt/EOD messages
- [sse_manager.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/alerts/sse_manager.py) — Redis Pub/Sub → SSE
- [signal_pipeline.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/engine/signal_pipeline.py) — End-to-end orchestrator
- Dashboard with live KPIs + signal feed + risk panel

### Phase 4 — Features
- [trades.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/api/routers/trades.py) — Trade journal with auto P&L
- [backtest_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/engine/backtest_engine.py) — Full backtest with Sharpe, drawdown, profit factor
- [backtest.py](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/backend/app/api/routers/backtest.py) — Backtest API with DB persistence

### Phase 5 — Hardening
- Settings page with editable risk parameters
- Login page with JWT auth
- Windows batch files: [start.bat](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/start.bat), [run.bat](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/run.bat), [stop.bat](file:///c:/Users/mohd9/OneDrive/Desktop/My_project/Stock_analysis/stop.bat)

---

## How to Start

```bat
:: First-time setup (auto migrations + seed + download)
start.bat

:: Daily quick start
run.bat

:: Stop all services
stop.bat
```

| Endpoint | URL |
|----------|-----|
| Dashboard | http://localhost:3000 |
| API Docs | http://localhost:8000/docs |
| Login | Username: `trader` / Password: `quantdss2025` |
